it.unimi.di.law.bubing.sieve

Class IdentitySieve<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unimi.di.law.bubing.sieve.AbstractSieve<K,V>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public final class IdentitySieve<K,V>
extends AbstractSieve<K,V>
    A sieve that simply (and immediately) copies enqueued keys to the new flow receiver.

    Note that instances of this class call AbstractSieve.NewFlowReceiver.prepareToAppend() in the constructor only, and AbstractSieve.NewFlowReceiver.noMoreAppend() in the method close() only.
